## üé® Design Principles

1. **Automation Over Customization** - Make decisions FOR users, not WITH them
2. **Accessibility-First** - WCAG AAA, triple input modality (voice/button/text)
3. **Single-Screen Flow** - No navigation, no tabs, vertical scroll only
4. **Instant Value** - Grocery list first, details second
5. **Graceful Degradation** - Works even if components fail

